{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id621f0b29-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t25/s261"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"261"},"text":"§ 261.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Power to appoint traders with Indians","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Commissioner of Indian Affairs shall have the sole power and authority to appoint traders to the Indian tribes and to make such rules and regulations as he may deem just and proper specifying the kind and quantity of goods and the prices at which such goods shall be sold to the Indians.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id621f0b2a-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1876-08-15/ch289/s5"},"text":"Aug. 15, 1876, ch. 289, § 5","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/19/200"},"text":"19 Stat. 200","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id621f0b2b-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"execDoc","id":"id621f0b2c-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Executive Documents","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"transferOfFunctions","id":"id621f0b2d-4962-11f1-add1-b56d3fa293fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Transfer of Functions","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For transfer of functions of other officers, employees, and agencies of Department of the Interior, with certain exceptions, to Secretary of the Interior, with power to delegate, see Reorg. Plan No. 3 of 1950, §§ 1, 2, eff. ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1950-05-24"},"text":"May 24, 1950","children":[],"tail":", 15 F.R. 3174, "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/64/1262"},"text":"64 Stat. 1262","children":[],"tail":", set out in the Appendix to Title 5, Government Organization and Employees."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
